Company Overview of Walgreens Boots Alliance Holdings LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Walgreens Boots Alliance Holdings LLC was formerly known as WAB Holdings LLC. The company was incorporated in 2013 and is based in Deerfield, Illinois. Walgreens Boots Alliance Holdings LLC operates as a subsidiary of Walgreens Boots Alliance, Inc.


